Package ezvcard.io.chain

Contains classes used in the chaining API.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChainingHtmlParser<T extends ChainingHtmlParser<?>>
    Chainer class for parsing hCards (HTML-encoded vCards).
    ChainingHtmlStringParser
    Chainer class for parsing hCards (HTML-encoded vCards) from strings.
    ChainingHtmlWriter
    Chainer class for writing hCards (HTML-encoded vCards).
    ChainingJsonParser<T extends ChainingJsonParser<?>>
    Chainer class for parsing jCards (JSON-encoded vCards).
    ChainingJsonStringParser
    Chainer class for parsing jCards (JSON-encoded vCards) from strings.
    ChainingJsonWriter
    Chainer class for writing jCards (JSON-encoded vCards).
    ChainingTextParser<T extends ChainingTextParser<?>>
    Chainer class for parsing traditional, plain-text vCards.
    ChainingTextStringParser
    Chainer class for parsing traditional, plain-text vCards from strings.
    ChainingTextWriter
    Chainer class for writing traditional, plain-text vCards.
    ChainingXmlMemoryParser
    Chainer class for parsing xCards (XML-encoded vCards) from strings or DOMs.
    ChainingXmlParser<T extends ChainingXmlParser<?>>
    Chainer class for parsing xCards (XML-encoded vCards).
    ChainingXmlWriter
    Chainer class for writing xCards (XML-encoded vCards).
